{"tid":1233321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽返許冠傑首洋紫荊，真係好感動","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:19:52.000Z","uid":138654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c95b35d1cfa3bdf5afa904f9b885e773e7f74629","tid":1233321,"uid":138654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:16:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jvUYsHMIJC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjvUYsHMIJC4&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4QRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=0e948ee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jvUYsHMIJC4</a><br />\n-<br />\n霓虹橙光 購物天堂<br />\n自由都市 百業繁旺<br />\n捕魚小島 遍歷風浪<br />\n在地球一小角<br />\n卻負名望 在東方<br />\n有粒珍珠閃閃發光<br />\n外地人都嚮往要看看<br />\n這獨特社會香港<br />\n在香港 你我的家鄉香港<br />\n艷麗洋紫荊到處盛放<br />\n滿眼儘是好風光 為未來香港<br />\n抱著希望 共謀方法 使它永安<br />\n路仍康莊那有驚惶<br />\n望破萬重浪 在東方<br />\n有粒珍珠閃閃發光<br />\n為未來香港再努力幹<br />\n不斷地發展使它更光 互相幫<br />\n困境風浪一起去檔<br />\n讓洋紫荊永遠盛放<br />\n永遠是原狀 香港<br />\n願明天香港也是天堂<br />\n定能看得見一點曙光<br />\n-<br />\n雖然呢首歌已經好耐之前<br />\n但佢推出個陣，香港真係一個好繁榮既城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550bec771d9f9911923a2f654cf77ceea9599a91","tid":1233321,"uid":138654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"推到更加多香港人聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289907ecfe08050ce87cba63b38bf1163eb6b563","tid":1233321,"uid":138654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:18:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdc1a6d37051d298da99e5be71c0403e35b6c93","tid":1233321,"uid":138654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:18:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"